			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    full warrior epic weapon quest</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=526382"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:">greatstub lvl60</a> | 
		                        12/4/2001 2:41:26 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
  Recover Unjeweled Dragon Head Hilt from bottom of Lake Rathe beneath the flaming Aviak tower. <BR>
  Obtain Diamond.  <BR>
  Obtain Black Sapphire.  <BR>
  Obtain Jacinth.  <BR>
  Turn in all four items to Wenden BlackHammer in East Freeport to create the Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt.  <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
 <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
  Retrieve Damaged Dragon Head Hilt from the Chessboard in Timorous Deep (-6500, 3000). <BR>
  Loot a Monocle from a Mountain Giant Patriarch (Dreadlands).  <BR>
  Give Monocle to giant, Mentrax Mountainbone, in Frontier Mountains giant fortress in return for Rejesiam Ore. <BR>
  Loot Ball of Everliving Golem from either Fright, Dread, or Terror in the Plane of Fear.  <BR>
  Turn in Hilt, Ore, and Ball to Wenden BlackHammer in East Freeport to create a Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt. <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
 <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Ancient Sword Blade<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
  Purchase a Keg of Vox Tail Ale...can be purchased from vendors throughout Norrath (Freeport Port Authority).  <BR>
  Loot a Block of Permafrost from an Ice Giant within Permafrost.  <BR>
  Purchase or create 2 Rebreathers (made through Tinkering skill and sold for 2-3k each).  <BR>
  Turn in all four items to Denken Strongpick on aviak island in the Ocean of Tears to receive Ancient Sword Blade.  <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
 <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Ancient Blade<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
  Loot the Ancient Blade from Sarnak Queen of Chardok.  <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
 <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
The Red Scabbard<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
  Obtain Wax Sealed Note from Kargek Redblade in East Freeport.  <BR>
  Deliver the Note to an ogre named Oknoggin in Feerrott who can be found standing next to a stone bridge. Receive a Tiny Lute in exchange for the Note.  <BR>
  Return the Tiny Lute to Kargek Redblade in exchange for a Book.  <BR>
  Deliver the Book to Tenal Redblade in East Karana who can be found at the bottom of the chasm near HH zone. Receive a Frozen War Totem in exchange for the Book. <BR>
  Loot a Heart of Frost from a goblin wizard in Permafrost.  <BR>
  Turn in the Frozen War Totem and Heart of Frost to Tenal Redblade in exchange for a Totem of Fiery War.  <BR>
  Loot a Red Scale from Nagafen (Solusek), Zordakilicus Ragefire (Solusek), Talendor (Skyfire), or Nortlav Scalekeeper (The Hole).  <BR>
  Loot a Green Scale from Severilous of Emerald Jungle.  <BR>
  Turn in the Red Scale, Green Scale, and Totem of Fiery War to Tenal in exchange for The Mark of the Sword.  <BR>
  Loot the Hand of the Maestro from the Hand that spawns when Maestro is killed in the Plane of Hate.  <BR>
  Turn in the Hand and the Mark of the Sword to Tenal in exchange for a Note to Kargek.  <BR>
  Loot a Spiroc Wingblade from the Spiroc Lord in the Plane of Air.  <BR>
  Turn in the Note and Spiroc Wingblade to Kargek Redblade in East Freeport to receive the Red Scabbard.  <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
 <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
VICTORY!<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
  Obtain Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt.  <BR>
  Obtain Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt.  <BR>
  Obtain Ancient Sword Blade.  <BR>
  Obtain Ancient Blade.  <BR>
  Obtain Red Scabbard.  <BR>
  Combine all five items to create Jagged Blade of War!!!  <BR>

